import React, { Component } from "react"
import { Link, withRouter } from "react-router-dom"
import { Wrap, Left, Right, Item } from "./styles/navbar"
import NavButton from "./Button"

class Navbar extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Wrap>
        <Left>
          <Link to="/">
            <Item href="/">BestTraveller</Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/">
            <Item>Home</Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/packages">
            <Item>Packages</Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/about-us">
            <Item>About us</Item>
          </Link>
          <Link to="/contact-us">
            <Item>Contact us</Item>
          </Link>
        </Left>
        <Right>
          <NavButton />
        </Right>
      </Wrap>
    )
  }
}

export default withRouter(Navbar)
